  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy, safety, and dose-response of nalmefene hydrochloride at 10 mg and 20 mg in
      patients with alcohol dependence will be evaluated in a multicenter, randomized,
      double-blind, placebo-controlled, 3-parallel-group comparative trial. The superiority of
      nalmefene hydrochloride at 20 mg to placebo will be verified in terms of reduction of alcohol
      consumption.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
